dwm_vol - dynamic sound
====================
dwm_vol is sound manage util for dwm.


Requirements
------------
In order to build dwm_vol you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (dwm_vol is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install dwm_vol
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running dwm_vol
-------------
See the man page for details.
